Title: making a dream reality
DateModified: '2019-02-16'
DatePublished: '2019-02-16'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/making-a-dream-reality
SetInCountry: Afghanistan
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Mohammad Kazim  Madadi
AuthorCountry: Afghanistan
Text: this is the story of a young man from the disaster place of the world, as I
  live in a country that really is disaster and blood country that every day hundred
  people are killed, this is what we grew with and faced with our soul. In spite of
  these, still there are dreams to make a reality. from the childhood I dreamed that
  to free my soul from everything banned to dream, it was/is dream to go outside and
  take pictures from beauty of Natures and write what I see, look for beauty of oceans,
  Mountains, falls, ancient places, sightseeing places and lot to more
